snippet.title: Second Wave - Official Xbox Announcement Trailer | ID@Xbox Showcase
snippet.description:
Second Wave, an upcoming free-to-play online multiplayer hero-based shooter MOBA from developer Challengers Games, is coming to Xbox Series X/S. Step into the world of Armantia, meet the characters, and see them in action in this latest Second Wave trailer, and become a legendary Hero or Exile to fight an endless war for The Arcane Stone, a mystical artifact that has helped Armantia advance in both Science and Technology.

#IGN #Gaming #Xbox
